    "last_activity_date" : 1653546453,
    "creation_date" : 1653546453,
    "answer_id" : 72387616,
    "question_id" : 6056124,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>The method of compiling the inserted object declaration is not found in the class file. The method name of the object for which the metaclass information is not obtained is reflected at runtime. According to the official description, the method signature of the object is implicitly extended, which may be allowed by the JVM runtime mechanism</p>\n"
  } ],
